O Bond，<br />\n否則唔應該睇coupon rate而係應該睇yield to maturity<br />\n如果yield係5%，一年後到期<br />\n100萬每年就有5萬蚊息，<br />\n到期連埋息拎返105萬<br />\n<br />\n不過宜家唔買B rate或以下嘅bond基本上冇乜肉食</blockquote><br />\n明白 多謝詳細解答 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無新加坡bond既list可以睇睇 求link</blockquote><br />\n其實fundsupermart同bondsupermart嘅母公司就係ifast<br />\n所以你上bondsupermart就可以睇到哂ifast買到啲咩bond<br />\n不過部份show出黎嘅bond唔算有好多成交，想買都未必有貨<br />\n至於bond express (即係USD100,000入場) on list嘅債暫時有12隻<br />\n如果自己搵到啲債唔係on list都可以俾ISIN code佢地要求加返<br />\n淨係計bond express嗰堆債嘅yield就由3.17%至7.59%不等<br />\n<br />\nIB都可以買到啲門檻極低嘅美債，不過要留意呢啲債嘅rating通常比較差<br />\n之前玩具反斗城都係入場門檻極低嘅美債嚟，不過因為loan唔掂破左產"},{"pid":"72d09b8d438b863ed9097adc62903c05ec5f6759","tid":483748,"uid":146720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T00:07:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我班朋友全部都債務遺約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地買左d乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d4770e67c0f6ddac8ba3f380e59cc98f54e45f","tid":483748,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T00:14:46.000Z","msg":"要好小心"},{"pid":"5322a9d85d37a96baeeade070417181e398f23e8","tid":483748,"uid":146720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6bf8f9b1e9a5120f8a7f20adca44756453dca74","tid":483748,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T15:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我班朋友全部都債務遺約<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地買左d